        </item>
        <item>
            <title>議員指廚餘回收設施不敷應用　公屋居民不懂用二維碼開廚餘回收桶</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/smart-food-waste-bin/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=smart-food-waste-bin</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/smart-food-waste-bin/life-tech/smartcity/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 09:17:07 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智能廚餘回收桶]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1229891</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>立法會議員陳凱欣表示，目前香港廚餘回收設施嚴重不足，部分公屋智能廚餘回收桶長期飽和，有機會引起衞生問題，因此建議當局加派人手協助居民。</p><p>立法會議員陳凱欣接受港台節目《千禧年代》採訪時表示，早前她曾經到深水埗元州邨視察廚餘回收情況，發現部分居民不懂得如何掃描二維碼使用智能廚餘回收桶，所以就直接將廚餘棄置於回收桶旁邊，或附近的垃圾桶，引起衞生問題。</p><p>陳凱欣認為，市民棄置廚餘高峯期普遍屬午餐及晚飯後，因此建議政府在高峯期加派人手從旁協助居民使用及加快清理廚餘回收桶。陳凱欣另外又指，智能廚餘回收桶不足應付需求，目前兩幢公屋大廈共用一部智能廚餘回收桶已有飽和情況，如附近大廈居民希望回收廚餘，就無法使用公屋內的廚餘回收桶。</p><p>圖片、資料來源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1749235-20240417.htm">RTHK</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/smart-food-waste-bin/life-tech/smartcity/">議員指廚餘回收設施不敷應用　公屋居民不懂用二維碼開廚餘回收桶</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/smart-food-waste-bin/life-tech/smartcity/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>全港戲院日開始售票，網民：「銀行已扣錢但未收到確認電郵」</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/cinema-day-2024/movie-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=cinema-day-2024</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/cinema-day-2024/movie-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 07:30:28 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影視娛樂]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[全港戲院日]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1229900</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>香港戲院商會繼去年後再度宣佈舉辦「全港戲院日」，4 月 21 日當日全港 63 間戲院所有電影票價劃一售 30 元。今日中午 12 時起各大戲院網站開始售票，小編剛剛（13:53）嘗試到其中一間影院網站排隊，留意到前面有逾 6,000 人排隊，場面墟冚。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229902" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240417135258-694x458.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="458" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240417135258-694x458.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240417135258.jpg 1277w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲小編剛剛嘗試到其中一間影院網站排隊，留意到前面有逾 6,000 人排隊</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229927" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/1-3-391x580.jpg" alt="" width="391" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/1-3-391x580.jpg 391w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/1-3.jpg 607w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 391px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有網友 12 時許嘗試排隊，前面有近 20000 人</p><p>LIHKG 討論區有網民表示，在正式開售（12:00）前在戲院應用程式已經買到戲飛。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229928" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2-2-672x580.jpg" alt="" width="672" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2-2-672x580.jpg 672w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/2-2.jpg 883w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 672px" /></p><p>有網民表示 30 元可以看 imax 電影，如果不需在門市排隊就化算；另外有網民指已成功購買 imax 戲飛， 連同手續費則是 40 元。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229929" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/3-2-694x179.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="179" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/3-2-694x179.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/3-2.jpg 882w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229930" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/4-1-694x182.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="182" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/4-1-694x182.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/4-1.jpg 885w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>有人歡喜有人愁，有網民表示已經去到銀行應用程式確認付款的階段，但回到購票網頁就只看見白畫面，亦沒有收到任何確認電郵。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229931" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/5-1-675x580.jpg" alt="" width="675" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/5-1-675x580.jpg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/5-1.jpg 868w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 675px" /></p><p>下面有網民回應表示自己亦遇到同樣情況，銀行顯示已經收取相關費用，但就沒有收到確認購票電郵。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229932" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/6-694x517.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="517" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/6-694x517.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/6.jpg 872w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>有網民稱，以往「買一送一」優惠，每張戲飛計算下來也只僅是 30 餘元，無必要特地去搶，又指輪候時間過長，寧願原價購買。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229933" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/7-694x179.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="179" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/7-694x179.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/7.jpg 878w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229935" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/9-694x151.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="151" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/9-694x151.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/9.jpg 881w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>另外亦有網民指，喜歡看電影的朋友應該不會購買這次戲院節的戲飛。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229934" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/8-694x249.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="249" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/8-694x249.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/8.jpg 878w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>「全港戲院日」為「香港流行文化節 2024 」的一部份，當日不設長者、小童及學生優惠，而所有戲院優惠及電影贈券亦不適用。如長者首場優惠票價已低於 30 元，售價將維持不變。30 元的優惠票價同時適用於 IMAX、4DX 等戲票。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3676172">LIHKG</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/11/cinema-day/movie-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">4 月 21 日全港戲院日，票價劃一 30 元</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/cinema-day-2024/movie-2/">全港戲院日開始售票，網民：「銀行已扣錢但未收到確認電郵」</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/cinema-day-2024/movie-2/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>網民：蔚來 AI 令離婚率上升，能列舉誰坐過副駕駛位</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/nio-car-raise-divorce-rate-said-chinese-twitter-user/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=nio-car-raise-divorce-rate-said-chinese-twitter-user</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/nio-car-raise-divorce-rate-said-chinese-twitter-user/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 05:48:44 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[NIO]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[蔚來汽車]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1229879</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>人工智能日新月異，現在很多電動車也內置人工智能助手，能夠智能調節車內温度、調校各種設定，甚至可以自動泊車，為駕駛者和乘客提供更方便的駕駛和乘坐體驗。不過近日有中國網民就發現，中國蔚來電動車內置的「人工智能車載系統」除了上述功能外，更可以化身私家偵探，替用家「捉姦」。</p><p>X（前稱 Twitter） 用户 @xiaojingcanxue 日前發文表：「蔚來人工智能能夠大幅拉昇離婚率」，並附上一條使用蔚來人工智能的影片。影片中可見拍攝人問蔚來人工智能本週有幾多個人坐個副駕駛位置，蔚來人工智能誠實地回應指，這個星期坐在副駕駛的有拍攝者的朋友李先生、同事王女士及一位不認識的先生，甚至能夠列舉出這幾位副駕駛座乘客甚麼時候乘車，在車廂做了甚麼。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229881" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glpcis7bgaaav5f-264x580.jpg" alt="" width="264" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glpcis7bgaaav5f-264x580.jpg 264w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glpcis7bgaaav5f-scaled.jpg 409w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 264px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://twitter.com/xiaojingcanxue/status/1779981255540633740">xiaojingcanxue@X</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229882" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glpcjp7a0aawdme-264x580.jpg" alt="" width="264" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glpcjp7a0aawdme-264x580.jpg 264w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glpcjp7a0aawdme-scaled.jpg 409w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 264px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://twitter.com/xiaojingcanxue/status/1779981255540633740">xiaojingcanxue@X</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229884" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glpconiauaefak3-264x580.jpg" alt="" width="264" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glpconiauaefak3-264x580.jpg 264w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glpconiauaefak3-scaled.jpg 409w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 264px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://twitter.com/xiaojingcanxue/status/1779981255540633740">xiaojingcanxue@X</a></p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="zh" dir="ltr">離婚神器，蔚來人工智能車載系統視頻演示。 <a href="https://t.co/Q9t1dbcmjR">pic.twitter.com/Q9t1dbcmjR</a></p><p>&mdash; 小徑殘雪 (@xiaojingcanxue) <a href="https://twitter.com/xiaojingcanxue/status/1779981255540633740?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">April 15, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>有網民回應指，這個發現不僅會令蔚來銷量大跌，甚至會影響其他新款電動車的銷量。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229886" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240417125604-694x251.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="251" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240417125604-694x251.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240417125604.jpg 742w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>有網民認為車內人工智能監視着一舉一動，非常可怕。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1229887" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240417125719-694x111.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="111" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240417125719-694x111.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/20240417125719.jpg 751w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://twitter.com/xiaojingcanxue/status/1779979963921547667">xiaojingcanxue@X</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/18/change-face-with-ai/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】Change Face With AI 換臉術，一鍵即換頭</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/19/openai-gpt-store-2/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】GPT Store 正式開放 ChatGPT AI 女朋友 + 一張相幫你諗食譜</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/16/ai-hallucination/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">全球最大避險基金橋水用 AI 投資，或有機會出現「AI 幻覺」虛假資訊</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/17/nio-car-raise-divorce-rate-said-chinese-twitter-user/fun-tech/">網民：蔚來 AI 令離婚率上升，能列舉誰坐過副駕駛位</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
